<div id="zh-question-title" data-editable="false">

<h2 class="zm-item-title zm-editable-content">

<a href="/question/30172029">Excel 单元格中的下三角箭头是做什么用的？如何实现？</a>

</h2>
</div>
<div id="zh-question-detail" class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="4251198" data-action="/question/detail">

<div class="zm-editable-content"><img src="//pic4.zhimg.com/2baddb9ecc666cf44550a233ce340973_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="732" data-rawheight="613" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" data-original="//pic4.zhimg.com/2baddb9ecc666cf44550a233ce340973_r.jpg"><br>第一排的表格有一个下三角箭头，<br>可以通过该单元格来筛选某一列的的信息。</div>


</div>
<div class="zm-item-meta zm-item-comment-el clearfix" id="zh-question-meta-wrap">
<div class="zm-meta-panel">

<a href="#" name="addcomment" class="toggle-comment meta-item">
