<div class="answer-head">
<div class="zm-item-answer-author-info">
<h3 class="zm-item-answer-author-wrap">


<a data-tip="p$t$kaiserwang730"
class="zm-item-link-avatar"
href="/people/kaiserwang730">
<img src="//pic1.zhimg.com/21cb65b48_s.jpg"
class="zm-list-avatar"
data-source="//pic1.zhimg.com/21cb65b48_s.jpg" />
</a>



<a data-tip="p$t$kaiserwang730" href="/people/kaiserwang730">Kaiser</a>，<strong title="天亮了" class="zu-question-my-bio">天亮了</strong>

</h3>
<a href="javascript:;" name="collapse" class="collapse meta-item zg-right"><i class="z-icon-fold"></i>收起</a>
</div>
<div class="zm-item-vote-info " data-votecount="176">

<span class="voters">
<span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$yiye-zhi-qiu-yu" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/yiye-zhi-qiu-yu" class="zg-link" title="一夜知秋雨">一夜知秋雨</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$li-an-dong-99" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/li-an-dong-99" class="zg-link" title="李安东">李安东</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$rang-wan-qi" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/rang-wan-qi" class="zg-link" title="让万奇">让万奇</a></span>
</span>


<a href="javascript:;" class="more"> 等人赞同</a>


</div>
</div>
<div class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="4251198" data-action="/answer/content">

<div class=" zm-editable-content clearfix"><p>这个是数据有效性（Validation）和筛选（Filter）。</p><br><p>首先建立数据有效性，选中一列如H，点击【数据有效性】：</p><noscript><img src="//pic4.zhimg.com/20241edc890f8ed4976aa94e340c61a3_b.jpg" data-rawheight="324" data-rawwidth="685" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="685" data-original="//pic4.zhimg.com/20241edc890f8ed4976aa94e340c61a3_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawheight="324" data-rawwidth="685" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="685" data-original="//pic4.zhimg.com/20241edc890f8ed4976aa94e340c61a3_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="//pic4.zhimg.com/20241edc890f8ed4976aa94e340c61a3_b.jpg"><br><br><p>在允许数据中选择序列（List），右边会出现一个下拉菜单（In-cell dropdown）选项。</p><noscript><img src="//pic3.zhimg.com/21418466bd1c86d76f300c89db153c76_b.jpg" data-rawheight="348" data-rawwidth="379" class="content_image" width="379"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawheight="348" data-rawwidth="379" class="content_image lazy" width="379" data-actualsrc="//pic3.zhimg.com/21418466bd1c86d76f300c89db153c76_b.jpg"><br><p>在【来源】中输入这一列单元格中可能出现的数据，以逗号分隔。</p><ul><li>注：只识别英文逗号。</li></ul><br><p>当选中H列单元格之后，右侧会出现一个向下的三角箭头：</p><noscript><img src="//pic3.zhimg.com/b021988de3cc1c579642077cc88c8b82_b.jpg" data-rawheight="198" data-rawwidth="197" class="content_image" width="197"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawheight="198" data-rawwidth="197" class="content_image lazy" width="197" data-actualsrc="//pic3.zhimg.com/b021988de3cc1c579642077cc88c8b82_b.jpg"><br><p>可以直接用鼠标点击输入，而不在预设序列中的内容则无法强行输入。<br><noscript><img src="//pic4.zhimg.com/80b2eb7b32b57a8d3867925774b7274f_b.jpg" data-rawheight="334" data-rawwidth="211" class="content_image" width="211"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawheight="334" data-rawwidth="211" class="content_image lazy" width="211" data-actualsrc="//pic4.zhimg.com/80b2eb7b32b57a8d3867925774b7274f_b.jpg"><br></p><p>最后，选中一个单元格再点击【自动筛选】（AutoFilter）即可。</p><noscript><img src="//pic3.zhimg.com/3e1fcb79e323aa9b9b1905744be89162_b.jpg" data-rawheight="635" data-rawwidth="636" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="636" data-original="//pic3.zhimg.com/3e1fcb79e323aa9b9b1905744be89162_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawheight="635" data-rawwidth="636" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="636" data-original="//pic3.zhimg.com/3e1fcb79e323aa9b9b1905744be89162_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="//pic3.zhimg.com/3e1fcb79e323aa9b9b1905744be89162_b.jpg"><br><p>被筛选掉的行会自动折♂叠。</p><noscript><img src="//pic3.zhimg.com/fdd0bf53f6627a21a6dee064837c1076_b.jpg" data-rawheight="426" data-rawwidth="639" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="639" data-original="//pic3.zhimg.com/fdd0bf53f6627a21a6dee064837c1076_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawheight="426" data-rawwidth="639" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="639" data-original="//pic3.zhimg.com/fdd0bf53f6627a21a6dee064837c1076_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="//pic3.zhimg.com/fdd0bf53f6627a21a6dee064837c1076_b.jpg">


</div>

